{"type": "article", "id": 3221, "title": "直角粘钩", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-03T08:17:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232844WvbxSrl0iKGHt7OZ.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t我们的桌面上需要归置太多东西，电脑、鼠标、键盘、杯子等等好多生活杂物，如果再加一个占地方的头戴式耳机，是不是感觉更麻烦了？设计团队 WKRMN 日前带来一款名为 Sound Stripp 的直角形状粘钩，造型及其简洁，可以将其粘贴在电脑显示屏的一侧，顺手挂耳机。Sound Stripp 可承重约 1 磅，足以应对市面上近 95% 的耳机。此外，Sound Stripp 的好处还在于将其从电脑上取下时，不会留下任何粘贴痕迹。黑白两色可选，定价 7.5 美元，<a href=\"http://workerman.storenvy.com/collections/1353-featured/products/10425885-sound-stripp\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232843J0KzPxmjIO6ytBRQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523284332al5CerEjKN9h1i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.9984375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232843L8cbxwiGTHPoJkBY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232844RqxWpaA0itg2o1bh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.9984375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}